<div><a href="mailto:cluster@bioclust:%7E$" target="_blank">cluster@bioclust:~$</a> mpirun --hostfile /etc/openmpi/openmpi-default-hostfile -np 17 /mnt/projects/PS3Cluster/Benchmark/pi<br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
